  "title": "Business Development Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>KEY ROLES AND RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop and execute business development strategies to achieve sales targets and drive revenue growth.</li>\n  <li>Identify new market opportunities and build a pipeline of potential clients in the banking, treasury, and fintech sectors.</li>\n  <li>Manage day to day project activities including scheduling, coordinating and monitoring and reporting update of projects</li>\n  <li>Monitor and ensure compliance to applicable scope of work, codes, practices, QA/QC policies, performance standards and specifications</li>\n  <li>Be the primary focal point between various parties</li>\n  <li>Able to contribute in Project Management / Engineering &amp; Site Construction activities</li>\n  <li>Conduct technical review on design concept, engineering and operational matters on the project and related activities</li>\n  <li>Co-ordinate with O&amp;M, technical / engineering resources / contractors / authorities for execution of the project</li>\n  <li>Assist in development, scoping and establishing project budget, schedule and control measures</li>\n  <li>Review of feasibility studies and cost estimates on proposed investment</li>\n  <li>Provide any other support</li>\n</ul>",
